Install nodejs using:
	sudo add-apt-repository ppa:jerome-etienne/neoip && sudo apt-get update && sudo apt-get install nodejs
	or, if so inclined you can look up how to pull the latest build from git and make it

Start the server:
	open a command line to the folder with server.js
	enter: node server.js

Connect to server:
	telnet clients are used for now
	enter: telnet localhost 8124    to connect
	enter sample commands to show off narrow/broad casting


